add

public void add(Results results)
Adds (concatenates) the data series from the given Results to this Results. The total number of series in this Results will be increased by the number of series in the given Results.

Parameters:
results - The data to add. The internal data is copied by reference, if independent changes need to be made to either Results object then the Results passed by this parameter should be a copy, e.g. via the copy constructor Results(Results).

add

public void add(double[] seriesData,
                java.lang.String label)
Adds (concatenates) the given data to this Results. The total number of series in this Results will be increased by the number of series in the given Results.

Parameters:
seriesData - The data to add. This is only copied by reference.
label - The label for the added data series. May be null.
